data.description: You won't want to miss this beautiful acreage. Located on 5.36 acres m/l this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is sure to please. The main floor features a beautifully remodeled eat-in- kitchen with Oak cabinets and bamboo floors. The bamboo floors extend into a large foyer with laundry and a 1/2 bath. Upstairs has 4 bedrooms and an additional full bathroom. The upstairs bathroom was remodeled within the last 2 months with new flooring, vanity, and bathtub. Outside of the home you will find two outbuildings. The large shop features a concrete floor and electricity. There is an additional barn on the property that can be used for multiple purposes. Call the listing agent today to schedule a showing.
